{"tid":1219619,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣鎮暴服(防暴隊)繡員警編號明顯在左胸前和背後上方處","createTime":"2019-06-13T23:54:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T08:40:25.000Z","uid":35790,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1c09d085250baf391b35743b7f39041bfef0fcb0","tid":1219619,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T23:54:37.000Z","msg":"台灣鎮暴服繡員警編號<br />\n<br />\n群眾運動頻傳保安警察失控毆打民眾，但事後受害人無法辨認涉案警察，導致找不出元凶；警政署昨表示，已明令要求各警察機關在鎮暴服裝繡上員警編號，以接受各方檢驗。<span style=\"color: red;\">根據警政署公佈的新式鎮暴服裝，在員警左胸前和背後上方處，都繡有明顯的數字代碼，代表使用員警的個人服務單位和列冊資訊。</span><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_1197786_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_1197786_1.jpg&h=2175a754&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_1197786_2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_1197786_2.jpg&h=affaa0b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/paper/845036\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fpaper%2F845036&d=dLzfXDqznxc4YuOEPdKADQvpIPIfgcH1aomtamkqoQA%3D&h=b3865e92\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fpaper%2F845036&h=ffc21614\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/paper/845036</a>"},{"pid":"cbce45cafea8dba7de8a9b23870d94ace452fe9d","tid":1219619,"uid":160605,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T23:56:13.000Z","msg":"香港堆黑警<br />\n委任證呢？<br />\n黑警：問我上司"},{"pid":"e1ff93f872aa1f5570a0f6ab367b53e370004b5c","tid":1219619,"uid":35790,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T23:56:50.000Z","msg":"尋晚光明頂才子有講到<br />\n香港防暴隊制服及編號問題"},{"pid":"400dcddc59c3d4ed5b754781289b32f36a2fb1c8","tid":1219619,"uid":164920,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"cbce